                <h5><b>Baggage Allowance</b></h5>
                <p>Q. What if i exceed my free baggage weight Allowance?</p>
                <p>A. Additional weight in excess will be subjected to the prevailing excess baggage fee on a per kg basis. If you pre-booked your baggage online but checked-in with heavier baggage, you will also be charged an
                excess baggage fee for each additional kg, which varies depending on the airport from which you depart.</p>
            </div>
